This challenge need a web server. the below is how to setup.
[Ubuntu]
apt install libzbar0
apt install libzbar-dev
apt install zbar-tools
apt install python3-pip
pip3 install setuptools --upgrade
pip3 install zbarlight
pip3 install pillow

1. Install HTTP server.
2. input below command

$ cp qr.cgi to /usr/lib/cgi-bin/
$ cp flag to /usr/lib/cgi-bin/
$ chmod 666 /usr/lib/cgi-bin/flag

Please check the permission of flag file.
Player can't access the flag file in cg-bin.

